                <![CDATA[
                    
                    <p><a class="s_tag" href="https://www.ithome.com/" target="_blank">IT之家</a> 10 月 27 日消息，AOC“Q27G4XM”27&nbsp;英寸显示器现已在京东开售，<strong>这款显示器主打“2K 180Hz QD-Mini LED”，售价为&nbsp;1799&nbsp;元</strong>。</p><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://u.jd.com/KGuzrsN" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="800" src="https://img14.360buyimg.com/pop/jfs/t1/137108/34/49498/14639/67176a6fF6e959f36/0a34ee039c92c8f5.jpg" title="AOC“Q27G4XM”27 英寸显示器开售：2K 180Hz，1799 元" width="800" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">京东</span><span class="card-name"> AOC“Q27G4XM”显示器</span></span><span class="card-abstract"></span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price"> 1799 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">直达链接</span></span></span></span></a></dir><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1342" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/10/28e9846d-1cdb-4b66-95e7-5a4c86ef4c79.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="AOC“Q27G4XM”27 英寸显示器开售：2K 180Hz，1799 元" width="852" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1247" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/10/7716c4bd-06e0-4e69-8aa4-d4a17da39258.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="AOC“Q27G4XM”27 英寸显示器开售：2K 180Hz，1799 元" width="842" /></p><p>这款显示器采用&nbsp;2560x1440&nbsp;分辨率&nbsp;180Hz QD-Mini LED&nbsp;面板。拥有&nbsp;1152&nbsp;分区，亮度&nbsp;1200&nbsp;尼特，响应速度&nbsp;1ms，静态对比度 1000:1，支持&nbsp;10-Bit&nbsp;色彩，覆盖&nbsp;100% sRGB&nbsp;与&nbsp;99% DCI-P3 色域。</p><p>这款显示器支架支持倾斜 / 升降 / 旋转，显示器本体支持&nbsp;VESA 100x100mm&nbsp;壁挂，提供&nbsp;2&nbsp;个&nbsp;HDMI 2.0、1&nbsp;个&nbsp;DP 1.4、1&nbsp;个 3.5mm&nbsp;音频接口。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="912" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/10/91d02177-e40e-43f3-931b-cabcbb6f5014.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="AOC“Q27G4XM”27 英寸显示器开售：2K 180Hz，1799 元" width="788" /></p><p>IT之家附显示器参数信息如下：</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1054" src="https: